            <span class="conclusion-val">回国做 3–4 周实习，建立国内人脉，提前布局转正通道</span>
          </div>
          <div class="conclusion-row">
            <span class="conclusion-key">研二 6–8月</span>
            <span class="conclusion-val">美国暑期实习全力转正；国内暑期实习并行；秋招准备启动</span>
          </div>
          <div class="conclusion-row">
            <span class="conclusion-key">研二 7–8月</span>
            <span class="conclusion-val">大陆头部机构开放报名（不要错过）；香港早开岗位关注</span>
          </div>
          <div class="conclusion-row">
            <span class="conclusion-key">研二 9–11月</span>
            <span class="conclusion-val">三线并行：美国 full-time rolling + 香港招聘峰期 + 大陆秋招面试</span>
          </div>
          <div class="conclusion-row">
            <span class="conclusion-key">研二 11月–次年1月</span>
            <span class="conclusion-val">Offer 博弈期：理性比较，尽快锁定</span>
          </div>
          <div class="conclusion-row">
